Unquiet spirit
Discworld ritual help
Unquiet spirit

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Unquiet Spirit -- Recalls a recently departed spirit from the afterlife
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Unquiet spirit recalls a recently departed spirit from their particular after
life to perform tasks on your behalf. This ritual requires a dagger, a lit candle,
and a holy symbol. You also need a copy of the prayer 'Piercing the veil'.
.EP
